# Rain Prediction Model

This project is a simple web application that predicts whether it will rain based on various weather conditions. It uses a pre-trained machine learning model to make predictions.

## Features

- **Pressure**: Atmospheric pressure (in hPa)
- **Dewpoint**: Dew point temperature (in Celsius)
- **Humidity**: Relative humidity (in %)
- **Cloud**: Cloud cover (in oktas)
- **Sunshine**: Sunshine duration (in hours)
- **Windspeed**: Wind speed (in km/h)
        